ppeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://orbtr.net\">ORBTR.NET - Sales &amp; Marketing Wordpress Plugin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"admin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3375:\"<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4411 size-full\" src=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-announce.jpg\" alt=\"wordpress marketing plugin\" width=\"868\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-announce.jpg 868w, https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-announce-300x199.jpg 300w, https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-announce-630x418.jpg 630w, https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-announce-630x418-360x238.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 868px) 100vw, 868px\" /></p>\n<p>For some users of ORBTR, a WordPress marketing plugin, this will be an important and long-awaited update. We love getting real-time notifications when tracking sales leads, but sometimes those notifications aren&#8217;t always &#8220;leads&#8221; — sometimes they can be your vendors, business partners, or even internal employees who are being tracked by the ORBTR system and the number of email notifications you receive can become overwhelming.</p>\n<p>We are happy to report that ORBTR 3.1 solves that issue by incorporating a &#8220;Blacklist&#8221; functionality that allows you to add any email addresses to your ORBTR configuration that you do NOT want to receive notifications for. Just type or copy and paste them here under ORBTR &gt; Configuration (one email per line) and you will no longer receive notifications when that individual returns.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4412 size-full\" src=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss1.png\" alt=\"wordpress marketing plugin\" width=\"1200\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss1.png 1200w, https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss1-300x103.png 300w, https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss1-630x215.png 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></a></p>\n<p>You can also Blacklist or Unblock leads directly from the individual lead record as well, found under ORBTR &gt; All Records.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4413\" src=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss2.png\" alt=\"31-ss2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss2.png 1200w, https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss2-300x79.png 300w, https://orbtr.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/31-ss2-630x166.png 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This new feature gives you a lot more control over your email notifications and makes them more valuable and usable as you tweak your settings.</p>\n<p>ORBTR 3.1 also includes bug fixes.</p>\n<p>This update will be available today for all ORBTR Connect subscribers, just check your WordPress Plugins screen for the update of this WordPress marketing plugin.</p>\n<div id=\"themify_builder_content-4410\" data-postid=\"4410\" class=\"themify_builder_content themify_builder_content-4410 themify_builder themify_builder_front\">\n\n	</div>\n<!-- /themify_builder_content --><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://orbtr.net/blog/orbtr-3-1-includes-more-control-over-email-notifications/\">ORBTR 3.1 Includes More Control Over Email Notifications</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://orbtr.net\">ORBTR.NET - Sales &amp; Marketing Wordpress Plugin</a>.</p>\n\";