osocial support.</li>\r\n 	<li><u>Nonpartisanship</u>: ICF is an independent, nonpartisan, nonsectarian charity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTo learn more about the Iraqi Children Foundation, please visit their <a href=\"http://www.iraqichildren.org\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>website</u></strong></a><a href=\"http://www.iraqichildren.org\" target=\"_blank\">.</a> <em> </em>','Iraqi Children Foundation','','publish','closed','open','','iraqi-children-foundation','','','2017-01-12 11:25:46','2017-01-12 15:25:46','',63,'http://kmdig.com/client/bhdefense/?page_id=67',0,'page','',0),(68,1,'2014-08-25 16:02:10','2014-08-25 16:02:10','','Iraqi Children Foundation','','inherit','open','open','','67-revision-v1','','','2014-08-25 16:02:10','2014-08-25 16:02:10','',67,'http://kmdig.com/client/bhdefense/67-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2014-08-25 16:02:23','2014-08-25 16:02:23','<h2>BH Defense Risk Mitigation Partners Worldwide</h2>\r\n<strong>We’re not resellers, we’re reinventers.</strong> Through our partners, BH Defense can scale to meet virtually any risk mitigation challenge. Our partners also enable us to create proprietary solutions that aren’t out there in the marketplace. In fact, our strong partner relationships give us access to technologies that aren’t available to others—along with permission to literally take different technologies apart and put them back together in new ways without voiding warranties. Because BH Defense’s toolkit is so much bigger, we can make existing solutions smarter and we can accomplish things with surveillance, security and threat assessments that have never been done before.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-1840\" src=\"http://bhdefense.com/media/airpatrol1.png\" alt=\"airpatrol\" width=\"174\" height=\"60\" /> <img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-1841\" src=\"http://bhdefense.com/media/bosch1.png\" alt=\"bosch\" width=\"174\" height=\"60\" /> <img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-1843\" src=\"http://bhdefense.com/med