ross the enterprise and throughout the environment.','The Stakes','','inherit','open','open','','39-revision-v1','','','2014-09-11 11:44:02','2014-09-11 15:44:02','',39,'http://kmdig.com/client/bhdefense/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1747,1,'2014-09-11 11:50:20','2014-09-11 15:50:20','<h2>BH Defense Risk Mitigation Partners Worldwide</h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">TO COME FROM BHD: a short intro paragraph on why you use partners, how you choose them and vet them, the value of this for customers.</span>','Partners','','inherit','open','open','','69-revision-v1','','','2014-09-11 11:50:20','2014-09-11 15:50:20','',69,'http://kmdig.com/client/bhdefense/69-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1750,1,'2014-09-25 10:16:12','2014-09-25 14:16:12','<h2>BH Defense: A Broader Vision for Mitigating Risk</h2>\r\n<strong>BH Defense LLC is led by senior risk mitigation specialists and engineers</strong>. We are leading consultants in the field and we’re seasoned “on the ground,” ready to roll up our sleeves and clear away risks to improve the certainty of success even in the most difficult environments.\r\n<h3>BH Defense Leadership Team</h3>\r\n<strong>Charley Dublin, </strong><em>Managing Director</em>\r\n\r\nAs Managing Director, Mr. Dublin is the senior executive and technical lead responsible for operations, physical protection system design, personal protection programs, convoy security, facility security, force protection project management and critical infrastructure protection programs in Iraq for a variety of clients. He is a retired Marine Corps Infantry Officer with more than forty years’ experience developing physical security, decision support, crisis management, and critical infrastructure protection systems and programs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Jerry Durant, </strong>\r\n\r\nBrief description of what Jerry does for BH.\r\n\r\n<strong>Gary House, </strong><em>CIO</em>\r\n\r\nAs the Chief Information Officer, Mr. House plans, designs, and manages the BH Defense in