ments.\r\n<h2>Project Life Cycle Support</h2>\r\nBH Defense has the in-house expertise and technical resources to assist clients throughout the project life cycle as follows:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Project due diligence in advance of operations</li>\r\n	<li>Project infrastructure development</li>\r\n	<li>Project implementation and risk mitigation</li>\r\n	<li>Training and capacity development</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Support Sectors</h2>\r\nBH Defense is capable of providing consultative or direct project management support for the following infrastructure sectors:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\"Rule of Law\" Programs and judicial infrastructure</li>\r\n	<li>Transportation infrastructure to include ports and airports</li>\r\n	<li>Power transmission infrastructure to include generation and distribution</li>\r\n	<li>Community critical infrastructure protection and development</li>\r\n	<li>Training and capacity building across all infrastructure sectors</li>\r\n</ul>','Project Management','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2014-09-25 10:31:13','2014-09-25 14:31:13','',33,'http://kmdig.com/client/bhdefense/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1760,1,'2014-09-25 10:31:44','2014-09-25 14:31:44','<h2>BH Defense Construction Management Solutions</h2>\r\nBH Defense provides comprehensive project management/construction management (PM/CM) services for governments and organizations worldwide. Effectively tailored to achieve the client\'s cost, time and quality goals, BH Defense core strengths include the ability to adapt to a changing environment and solving the myriad problems unique to each new project. Our experience enables us to innovate, adapt, and overcome obstacles to the projects’ success.','Construction','','inherit','open','open','','35-revision-v1','','','2014-09-25 10:31:44','2014-09-25 14:31:44','',35,'http://kmdig.com/client/bhdefense/35-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1781,1,'2014-10-02 14:33:05','2014-10-02 18:33:05','','Screen Shot 2014-09-25 at 3.49.02 PM','','