 vendors.</strong> BH Defense draws on years of experience solving logistical challenges in difficult environments. We’ve mastered export and import restrictions on everything from construction supplies to IT equipment. We’ve carved out routes through even the most hostile territories. And we’ve built a network of third-party vendors we know we can trust because we’ve vetted them for so many years on so many tough assignments. So if you need to get something from point A to point B—fast, safe and sure—call BH Defense. We’ll roll up our sleeves immediately, make the calls, get a team organized and get your shipment in motion along with all the paperwork needed to meet legal requirements for all the agencies and jurisdictions involved. And your shipment will arrive when and where you need it. We’re certain, because we’ve done this work so many, many times with success.\r\n\r\n<strong>REAL-WORLD EXPERTISE:</strong> BH Defense managed all labor, equipment and supplies for force protection ant all Entry Control Points within the Baghdad IZ. BH Defense also constructed a man-camp to Support Regime Crimes Liaison Office (RCLO) operations and provide full life support for the camp, including food service, force protection systems O&amp;M, and static security.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Customers\" href=\"http://bhdefense.com/news/whitepapers-tools/\"><em><strong>To learn more, download our brochures on our Whitepapers &amp; Tools page</strong></em></a>','Logistics/Supply Chain','','inherit','closed','closed','','31-revision-v1','','','2016-12-20 17:06:02','2016-12-20 21:06:02','',31,'http://bhdefense.com/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1968,1,'2016-12-20 17:06:19','2016-12-20 21:06:19','<h2>BH Defense Project Management Solutions</h2>\r\n<strong>IT, construction, staffing, curriculum, you name it: we manage everything to get your project live.</strong> Through our own staff and our partners, BH Defense has access to extraordinary expertise and resources. So when we say we can manage every aspect of your project, you can count on it. In Iraq, for example, we were the prime contractor on a project to create a war college, and our project management way wasn’t just the needs analysis and CONOP: we managed the procurement of materials, permits and vendors; the construction process; the utility, water and power infrastructure; communications; HVAC; hiring the maintenance staff; hiring the instructors; and even developing the curriculum. Bottom line, no matter how difficult the project—or the environment—we manage it smoothly so you can get it “done.”\r\n\r\n<strong>REAL-WORLD EXPERTISE:</strong> BHD provided turnkey project management for events management, security and communications for major international military summits, including the Iraq Regional National Security Seminar and the Iraq National Security Seminar.\r\n<h2>Project Life Cycle Support</h2>\r\nBH Defense has the in-house expertise and technical resources to assist clients throughout the project life cycle as follows:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Project due diligence in advance of operations</li>\r\n 	<li>Project infrastructure development</li>\r\n 	<li>Project implementation and risk mitigation</li>\r\n 	<li>Training and capacity development</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Support Sectors</h2>\r\nBH Defense is capable of providing consultative or direct project management support for the following infrastructure sectors:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\"Rule of Law\" Programs and judicial infrastructure</li>\r\n 	<li>Transportation infrastructure to include ports and airports</li>\r\n 	<li>Power transmission infrastructure to include generation and distribution</li>\r\n 	<li>Community critical infrastructure protection and development</li>\r\n 	<li>Training and capacity building across all infrastructure sectors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title=\"Customers\" href=\"http://bhdefense.com/news/whitepapers-tools/\"><em><strong>To learn more, download our brochures on our Whitepapers &amp; Tools page</strong></em></a>','Project Management','','inherit','closed','closed','','33-revision-v1','','','2016-12-20 17:06:19','2016-12-20 21:06:19','',33,'http://bhdefense.com/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1969,1,'2016-12-20 17:06:35','2016-12-20 21:06:35','<h2>BH Defense Construction Management Solutions</h2>\r\nBH Defense provides comprehensive project management/construction management (PM/CM) services for governments and organizations worldwide. Effectively tailored to achieve the client\'s cost, time and quality goals, BH Defense core strengths include the ability to adapt to a changing environment and solving the myriad problems unique to each new project. Our experience enables us to innovate, adapt, and overcome obstacles to the projects’ success.\r\n\r\n<strong>REAL-WORLD EXPERTISE:</strong> BH Defense monitored local national laborers and contractors on a major Mideast construction project.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Customers\" href=\"http://bhdefense.com/news/whitepapers-tools/\"><em><strong>To learn more, download our brochures on our Whitepapers &amp; Tools page</strong></em></a>','Construction','','inherit','closed','closed','','35-revision-v1','','','2016-12-20 17:06:35','2016-12-20 21:06:35','',35,'http://bhdefense.com/35-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1970,1,'2016-12-20 17:06:51','2016-12-20 21:06:51','<h2>BH Defense Training Solutions</h2>\r\nOur innovative and time-tested approach implemented by highly experienced professionals ensures customer satisfaction in the government and commercial marketplace.\r\n\r\nBH Defense team members have a proven track record of training, mentoring, and leading high profile personal protection staff that secure top-level dignitaries globally.\r\n\r\nGlobally, we are prepared to embed international advisers with units throughout their rigorous training cycle and sensitive operations.\r\n<h3>BH Defense “Modus Operandi”</h3>\r\nWe employ highly qualified instructors in order to create specific curriculum for:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Host national Professional Military Education (PME)</li>\r\n 	<li>Operational training &amp; Tactical support to the U.S. Department of Defense, Department of State, host national Ministries of Defense and Ministries of Interior</li>\r\n 	<li>Advanced soldier and unit fire and maneuver training</li>\r\n 	<li>Advanced rural &amp; urban combat training</li>\r\n 	<li>Advanced intelligence, surveillance, and reconnaissance training</li>\r\n 	<li>Collection management training</li>\r\n 	<li>Technical support to Human Infrastructure Training (HUMINT)</li>\r\n 	<li>Long-range individual weapons training</li>\r\n 	<li>Target Acquisition training (TA)</li>\r\n 	<li>Movement to contact training</li>\r\n 	<li>Offensive and defensive operations training</li>\r\n 	<li>Specializing in Covert, overt, clandestine, and asymmetric warfare training</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBH Defense is committed to providing the intellectual knowhow and direct support necessary to enable our customers to successfully prosecute future missions and technical goals while working in non-permissive environments globally <em>“anytime anywhere”</em>.\r\n\r\n<strong>REAL-WORLD EXPERTISE:</strong> BH Defense trained and mentored the personal protection staff for a top-level dignitary. We hired instructors and created the curriculum for a Professional Military Education (PME) campus focused on developing Iraq’s military leadership to include administration, operations, facilities and teaching excellence.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Customers\" href=\"http://bhdefense.com/news/whitepapers-tools/\"><em><strong>To learn more, download our brochures on our Whitepapers &amp; Tools page</strong></em></a>','Training','','inherit','closed','closed','','37-revision-v1','','','2016-12-20 17:06:51','2016-12-20 21:06:51','',37,'http://bhdefense.com/37-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1971,1,'2016-12-20 17:09:08','2016-12-20 21:09:08','','microsoft-word-bh-d_9-reasons','','inherit','open','closed','','microsoft-word-bh-d_9-reasons','','','2016-12-20 17:09:08