stantly seeking self-improvement. I have experience living, working and driving in Middle East countries and understand the customs and courtesies of the Middle East. I am seeking a position overseas: South Sudan, Iraq, Afghanistan; I will consider any other positions in the Middle East, Africa, Europe, and Asia.\r\n\r\nFinally, I hope that this may lead to an interview so we can discuss a potential future I may have with your organization. If you have any question or to set up any interview, please call me at (601) 818-3036 or email me at vargas547_1999@yahoo.com . Thank you.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nRaymond J. Vargas JR\r\n\r\n\r\n'),(459,44,2,4,'http://bhdefense.com/media/gravity_forms/2-9e8f6889ccb9b37660bec9d400f884fa/2015/02/Raymond-Vargas-resume-OPs-2015.doc'),(460,45,2,1.3,'Keshawna'),(461,45,2,1.6,'DUBOSE'),(462,45,2,5.1,'3504 Parkway Terrace Dr apt  5'),(463,45,2,5.3,'Suitland'),(464,45,2,5.4,'Maryland'),(465,45,2,5.5,'20746'),(466,45,2,5.6,'United States'),(467,45,2,3,'(202)329-9319'),(468,45,2,2,'ktdubose@gmail.com'),(469,45,2,6,'2015-02-09'),(470,45,2,7,'Yes'),(471,45,2,8,'Yes'),(472,45,2,9,'Yes'),(473,45,2,4,'http://bhdefense.com/media/gravity_forms/2-9e8f6889ccb9b37660bec9d400f884fa/2015/02/dubose.keshawna-1.doc'),(474,46,1,4,'My name is Richard and I am Wordpress  security expert. While browsing your site bhdefense.com, I found that your site is vulnerable to hackers. I have prepared detailed security audit report for bhdefense.com. Please visit www.perfectwordpresssecurity.com/report/bhdefense.com  to view the security vulnerabilities to your website. I have also added screenshot of your website to show you that which pages can be accessed by hackers. Everyday 30000+ Wordpress sites are hacked! Your wordpress website should not be victim of one of those malicious attacks. If you have any questions, please feel free to email me for FREE consultancy at sales@perfectwordpresssecurity.com'),(475,47,1,4,'My name is Richard and I am Wordpress  security exp